Transaction
1. Write a query to implement the transaction process.
1.1) set autocommit off
1.2) set the transaction with specified name
1.3) Perform the transaction process
1.4) commit the process
1.5) set the transaction with specified name
1.6) Perform the transaction process
1.7) Rollback the process.
2. Write a query to implement the transaction process.
2.1) set autocommit off
2.2) set the save point with specified name
2.3) Perform the transaction process
2.4) commit the process
2.5) set the save point with specified name
2.6) Perform the transaction process
2.7) Rollback the process till the specified save point set in 2.5.
